WEBVTT

00:00:01.721 --> 00:00:04.181
Moram da vam priznam nešto:

00:00:04.181 --> 00:00:07.420
ja sam ovisnik o avanturi,

00:00:07.420 --> 00:00:09.859
i kao mali dečak,

00:00:09.859 --> 00:00:12.367
radije sam gledao kroz prozor

00:00:12.367 --> 00:00:15.101
ka pticama na drveću i nebu

00:00:15.101 --> 00:00:18.627
nego u tu dvodimenzionalnu tablu,

00:00:18.627 --> 00:00:21.208
na kojoj vreme stoji,

00:00:21.208 --> 00:00:23.953
a ponekad i umire.

00:00:23.953 --> 00:00:25.763
Moji učitelji su mislili da nešto

00:00:25.763 --> 00:00:28.930
sa mnom nije u redu
jer nisam pazio na času.

00:00:28.930 --> 00:00:31.560
Nisu pronašli ništa posebno loše